Package edu.ncsu.csc216.tracker.requirement

Package for the context and creation of requirements and commands. Requirement is the context and requirements for a Requirement while Command and RequirementState deal with the transition of the finite state machine
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RequirementState
    Interface for states in the Requirement State Pattern.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Command
    Objected used by the GUI to help the requirement object transition through states using the command enums.
    CommandTest
    Tester for the command object
    Requirement
    Context and object class for the Requirement class.
    RequirementTest
    Test the Requirement objects methods, including FSM transitions
